title: Meet the 2024 Tiny Desk Contest Community
description:
We received 6,600 entries to this year's Tiny Desk Contest. Meet the independent artists who make up the 2024 Tiny Desk Contest community -- and stay tuned for the winner reveal.

Soundtrack:
"What's it all mean," The Philharmonik
"SWIM!," Cleo Reed
"Haiku Nursery Rhyme," FORAGER
"Grateful," Jutaun

Watch these entries and more: npr.org/tinydeskcontest.
